msgid ""
"The largest refracting telescope in the world is at the *Yerkes Observatory* "
"in Williams Bay, Wisconsin. Built in 1897, it has a 1.02-m (40-in) objective "
"and a focal length of 19.36 m."
msgstr ""
"El mayor telescopio refractor del mundo está situado en el "
"<firstterm>Observatorio de Yerkes</firstterm>, en Williams Bay, Wisconsin. "
"Construido en 1897, posee un objetivo de 1,02 m (40 pulgadas) y una "
"distancia focal de 19,36 m."

